<br>
I had all the maps printed from EQ atlas, and I was terrified. I got to highpass and got lost, a kind mage helped me to high keep, bound me and led me to the EK zone.<br>
<br>
I remember running down the ramp in EK, absolutely terrified.. the people in that zone were all 18-25.. I was 8.. I was petrified of getting trampled hehe.<br>
<br>
Somehow I made it. Seeing the different landscapes for the very first time was an amazing experience. <p><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53989>Nahide' Altaica , Khala Dun Journeycat Champion of the 54th rank</a><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>
